00:00:12,636 --> 00:00:20,876
SEDAM SAMURAJA

3
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:55,570
U ranom šesnaestom vijeku,

4
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:58,730
Japan je bio u žaru borbe graðanskog rata ...

5
00:02:58,890 --> 00:03:01,970
i farmeri širom zemlje bili su ugnjetavani...

6
00:03:02,130 --> 00:03:05,410
od strane okrutnih bandita.

7
00:03:48,957 --> 00:03:52,237
Uzmimo i ovo selo!

8
00:03:55,477 --> 00:03:56,677
Cekaj!

9
00:03:57,037 --> 00:03:59,597
Krali smo rižu ovdje prošle jeseni

10
00:04:00,877 --> 00:04:03,117
Bojim se da još uvijek nemaju ništa

11
00:04:04,957 --> 00:04:07,597
Vratimo se kada
jecam sazri

12
00:04:40,845 --> 00:04:43,685
Zar nema Boga da nas zaštiti?

13
00:04:45,325 --> 00:04:47,685
Porez na zemlju!

14
00:04:47,845 --> 00:04:49,125
Prinudni rad!

15
00:04:49,285 --> 00:04:51,325
Rat!

16
00:04:51,525 --> 00:04:52,885
Suše!

17
00:04:53,125 --> 00:04:55,725
A onda, banditi!

18
00:04:58,725 --> 00:05:01,765
Bog sigurno želi da mi farmeri umremo od gladi!

19
00:05:02,005 --> 00:05:04,325
To je tocno, bolje da umremo

20
00:05:07,118 --> 00:05:08,518
Prestanite da se žalite!

21
00:05:08,758 --> 00:05:10,678
To nece pomoci!

22
00:05:11,638 --> 00:05:14,558
Hajdemo kod sudca za prekršaje!

23
00:05:14,678 --> 00:05:16,478
Da apeliramo kod njega!

24
00:05:17,558 --> 00:05:19,478
Koja je korist od toga?

25
00:05:19,678 --> 00:05:22,758
On bi došao samo kada bi
banditi otišli!

26
00:05:26,198 --> 00:05:30,518
Dajmo sve banditima!
Svu hranu koju posjedujemo!

27
00:05:31,118 --> 00:05:33,118
A onda se objesimo!

28
00:05:33,398 --> 00:05:36,598
To bi ga možda natjeralo
da radi!

29
00:05:48,087 --> 00:05:50,807
Napravimo koplja od bambusa

30
00:05:50,967 --> 00:05:53,887
Poubijajmo bandite,
pobijmo ih sve!

31
00:05:54,047 --> 00:05:55,887
Nece se više vracati,
ako ih sve pobijemo.

32
00:05:56,247 --> 00:05:57,647
Ne dopada mi se ova ideja.

33
00:06:02,967 --> 00:06:05,007
To je nemoguce!

34
00:06:06,407 --> 00:06:09,847
Možeš ubiti samuraja u begu-
ali ne i bandite!

35
00:06:10,047 --> 00:06:12,087
Prestani te!

36
00:06:12,247 --> 00:06:13,367
Ovo nije vrijeme za svaðu!

37
00:06:17,537 --> 00:06:20,977
Nemamo nikakve šanse protiv njih!

38
00:06:21,537 --> 00:06:23,817
Što bi bilo kada bi nas porazili?
Svi bismo bili ubijeni!

39
00:06:24,457 --> 00:06:26,057
Ubijaju cak i bebe u stomaku!

40
00:06:26,697 --> 00:06:27,177
Dosta!

41
00:06:27,977 --> 00:06:32,777
Bolje je ubiti ili biti ubijen,
nego da se osjecamo ovako

42
00:06:34,297 --> 00:06:36,777
Farmeri su roðeni da pate.

43
00:06:36,977 --> 00:06:38,457
To je naša sudbina.

44
00:06:41,097 --> 00:06:43,497
Docekajmo ih pokorno

45
00:06:44,337 --> 00:06:46,737
Predajmo naše usjeve.

46
00:06:46,937 --> 00:06:51,617
Samo ih preklinjite da ostave barem nešto
tako da nebismo umrli od gladi.

47
00:06:53,738 --> 00:06:56,698
Molimo ih na koljenima,
da bismo živjeli

48
00:06:58,523 --> 00:07:01,083
Mislite li da ce nas poslušati?.

49
00:07:01,283 --> 00:07:03,163
Zar ste zaboravili?

50
00:07:03,363 --> 00:07:06,563
Rižu koju jedemo, kako...

51
00:07:28,123 --> 00:07:29,883
Hajdemo kod Djeda!

52
00:07:30,083 --> 00:07:32,243
I zatražimo savjet!

53
00:08:38,354 --> 00:08:40,394
Pregovarajte sa njima. Ovisno sa kim
imate posla.

54
00:08:42,074 --> 00:08:43,594
Oni su gori od vukova.
Ako im date prst,

55
00:08:43,914 --> 00:08:45,354
uzet ce vam i ruku!

56
00:08:46,154 --> 00:08:47,434
Oni ne znaju za granicu.

57
00:08:47,754 --> 00:08:48,994
Doci ce opet na jesen!

58
00:08:49,194 --> 00:08:50,314
Ali ako izgubimo...Ha?

59
00:08:50,634 --> 00:08:51,434
Pa izgubili smo!

60
00:08:53,194 --> 00:08:55,114
Bez usjeva cemo svejedno umrijeti.

61
00:09:00,314 --> 00:09:01,314
Borit cemo se!

62
00:09:04,259 --> 00:09:06,539
To je suviše neodgovorno!

63
00:09:06,699 --> 00:09:09,379
Mi smo farmeri.
Ne znamo se boriti.

64
00:09:09,699 --> 00:09:11,339
Unajmit cemo samuraja!

65
00:09:12,019 --> 00:09:15,379
Unajmiti samuraja?
Prvi put cujem za tako nešto!

66
00:09:16,379 --> 00:09:20,219
Vidio sam svojim ocima.

67
00:09:21,259 --> 00:09:25,939
Kada je tvoje rodno selo spaljeno

68
00:09:26,979 --> 00:09:32,099
I dok sam bježao u ovo,
Vidio sam...

69
00:09:32,259 --> 00:09:38,139
jedno selo koje nije bilo spaljeno.
To selo je unajmilo samuraja

70
00:09:40,283 --> 00:09:43,723
Ali Djeda, postoje mnoge
vrste sela

71
00:09:43,883 --> 00:09:46,123
Mi jedemo kašu.
Kako cemo nahraniti samuraja?

72
00:09:46,283 --> 00:09:47,603
Mogli bismo jesti proso!

73
00:09:48,523 --> 00:09:51,483
Da li ce samuraj stati uz nas,
samo za hranu?

74
00:09:52,083 --> 00:09:53,643
Oni su jako ponosni!

75
00:09:54,283 --> 00:09:59,723
Naði gladnog samuraja!

76
00:10:02,163 --> 00:10:06,803
Cak i medvjedi izlaze iz šume,
kada su gladni

77
00:10:51,768 --> 00:10:53,808
Kakva neposlušnost!

78
00:10:55,168 --> 00:11:00,768
Koliko god da sam siromašan, ja nisam prosjak!

79
00:11:04,288 --> 00:11:05,008
Budalo!

80
00:11:12,408 --> 00:11:13,888
Upozorio sam te

81
00:11:48,115 --> 00:11:50,235
Sazrelo je

82
00:11:50,995 --> 00:11:53,915
Naravno.
Prošlo je deset dana.

83
00:11:54,195 --> 00:11:55,315
Što da radimo?

84
00:11:57,355 --> 00:12:00,835
Ovo je vrsta koja rano sazrijeva.
Nije kao naša!

85
00:12:04,595 --> 00:12:07,595
Mokar sam kao miš!

86
00:12:07,835 --> 00:12:10,555
Jeste li našli nekog jeftinog, jakog,
i voljnog samuraja?

87
00:12:50,859 --> 00:12:54,259
Neke ostatke.
Prodat cu ih jeftino

88
00:12:54,379 --> 00:12:55,379
To je smijurija!

89
00:12:56,699 --> 00:12:57,859
Što je tako smiješno?

90
00:12:58,019 --> 00:12:59,539
On je slijep!

91
00:13:00,419 --> 00:13:01,459
A ti?

92
00:13:01,579 --> 00:13:02,979
Ne, hvala.

93
00:13:03,099 --> 00:13:04,819
Radije bih jeo konjsku balegu.

94
00:13:09,459 --> 00:13:11,219
On je švorc!

95
00:13:11,659 --> 00:13:13,579
Sinoc sam ga opelješio.

96
00:13:13,779 --> 00:13:17,339
Potego je mac
pa smo ga pretukli.

97
00:13:17,539 --> 00:13:19,339
Švorc je na mrtvo.

98
00:13:25,323 --> 00:13:27,923
Oni jedu samo proso.

99
00:13:28,723 --> 00:13:30,203
Jeli to istina?

100
00:13:30,283 --> 00:13:34,523
Jedite pravilno ili
cete dobiti kokošje sljepilo!

101
00:13:34,723 --> 00:13:38,323
Možete ih imati za
šacicu riže.

102
00:13:44,563 --> 00:13:46,723
Vi i svi ostali.

103
00:14:05,861 --> 00:14:08,221
Kakvo rasipništvo!

104
00:14:08,581 --> 00:14:12,301
Sa tom rižom mogli bismo
dobiti cetrdeset zemicki!

105
00:14:12,781 --> 00:14:14,021
Prestani!

106
00:14:14,701 --> 00:14:16,221
Zar nisam u pravu?

107
00:14:17,701 --> 00:14:20,821
Budale su lude!

108
00:14:29,838 --> 00:14:34,358
Kakvo rasipništvo! Kakva ludost!

109
00:14:36,198 --> 00:14:39,918
Najeo se obilno.

110
00:14:40,398 --> 00:14:43,158
Napio se obilno.

111
00:14:43,318 --> 00:14:46,038
Onda me je pretukao i otišao.

112
00:14:47,118 --> 00:14:48,918
Mudar samuraj!

113
00:14:49,758 --> 00:14:53,518
Kako cudno, za razliku od onoga
što se pravi da spava!

114
00:14:54,398 --> 00:14:58,278
Hajdemo odavde!
Idemo kuci!

115
00:14:59,718 --> 00:15:00,718
On place!

116
00:15:01,438 --> 00:15:02,958
Nedostaje mu žena!

117
00:15:03,118 --> 00:15:05,278
Sve bih dao samo da ih vidim kako se vole!

118
00:15:07,318 --> 00:15:10,318
Hajdemo kuci! Molim vas!

119
00:15:10,518 --> 00:15:14,078
Idi kuci! Kako možeš unajmiti samuraja,
kad si ne možeš ni zemicke priuštiti

120
00:15:16,334 --> 00:15:20,774
Osim toga, mi nište ne znamo
o samurajima.

121
00:15:21,014 --> 00:15:24,054
Isto toliko znamo i sjemenu.

122
00:15:24,894 --> 00:15:28,774
Oni jaci su
izvan naše kontrole.

123
00:15:30,094 --> 00:15:34,774
Oni naizgled voljni su slabici!

124
00:15:44,014 --> 00:15:47,694
Sinoc sam poražen samo zato
što sam bio gladan.

125
00:15:48,974 --> 00:15:50,254
Lažov!

126
00:15:50,414 --> 00:15:52,014
Zato si imao novac za kockanje!

127
00:15:54,784 --> 00:15:57,304
Opet tražiš vraga?

128
00:15:58,944 --> 00:16:00,464
Tuca!

129
00:16:04,944 --> 00:16:06,544
Ovamo, ovamo!

130
00:16:16,824 --> 00:16:17,344
Prestanite!

131
00:16:17,624 --> 00:16:19,864
Tako je depresivno!

132
00:16:20,024 --> 00:16:21,224
Svirajte!

133
00:16:21,384 --> 00:16:22,744
Svirajte glasno! Mi vas podržavamo!

134
00:16:59,343 --> 00:17:02,383
Hoceš ici kuci!
A ipak...

135
00:17:03,143 --> 00:17:06,303
Ali nikada nisam bio u prilici
pregovarati sa njima!

136
00:17:06,703 --> 00:17:08,663
Što drugo možemo uciniti?

137
00:17:09,223 --> 00:17:11,943
Morate sami riješiti probleme sa banditima!

138
00:17:13,336 --> 00:17:14,296
U redu!

139
00:17:14,536 --> 00:17:15,456
Tako dakle!

140
00:17:24,216 --> 00:17:25,016
Ali -

141
00:17:26,336 --> 00:17:30,776
Što ceš im ponuditi ovog puta?

142
00:17:32,618 --> 00:17:34,858
Svoju kcer?

143
00:17:36,298 --> 00:17:38,738
Veoma je lijepa! Moglo bi i upaliti!

144
00:19:10,972 --> 00:19:12,892
Što se dogaða?

145
00:19:13,132 --> 00:19:14,892
U štali je lopov!

146
00:19:15,212 --> 00:19:17,252
Utrcao je unutra kada
su ga spazili!

147
00:19:39,804 --> 00:19:41,324
Koliko lopova?

148
00:19:42,284 --> 00:19:43,564
Samo jedan.

149
00:19:44,044 --> 00:19:45,124
Jedan?

150
00:19:47,124 --> 00:19:49,644
Pa što vas sprjecava?

151
00:19:49,884 --> 00:19:50,884
On ima prednost.

152
00:19:51,084 --> 00:19:53,564
Oteo je dijete.

153
00:19:54,124 --> 00:19:56,644
Kaže da ce ga ubiti ako napadnemo!

154
00:19:57,964 --> 00:19:59,964
Slušaj! Cuješ li to?

155
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:07,750
Jadno dijete!

156
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:14,910
Unutra su još od
sinoc. Jadno dijete!

157
00:20:15,430 --> 00:20:17,670
Glas mu je ogrubio!

158
00:20:21,934 --> 00:20:23,334
Sedam mu je godina.

159
00:20:24,814 --> 00:20:25,934
Jadni njegovi roditelji!

160
00:20:26,574 --> 00:20:29,694
Ali što nije u redu sa tim samurajem?
Brije glavu?

161
00:20:30,294 --> 00:20:31,174
Misterija.

162
00:20:31,734 --> 00:20:36,214
Obecao je da ce spasiti djecaka.
Tražio je dvije posude riže.

163
00:20:36,694 --> 00:20:40,174
Onda se poceo brijati
i zatražio je svecenicku odoru.

164
00:20:40,334 --> 00:20:41,494
Ne shvacam!

165
00:22:15,762 --> 00:22:17,282
Ovo je svecenik.

166
00:22:20,338 --> 00:22:22,218
Ja sam svecenik!

167
00:22:22,418 --> 00:22:24,138
Ne želim tebe!

168
00:22:25,867 --> 00:22:27,467
Ne brini.

169
00:22:27,747 --> 00:22:30,987
Djecak je sigurno izgladnio.

170
00:22:31,267 --> 00:22:33,387
Ne ulazi! Donio sam hranu

171
00:22:36,901 --> 00:22:39,221
Donio sam i za tebe!

172
00:22:46,198 --> 00:22:47,718
Uzmi!

173
00:22:48,638 --> 00:22:50,518
Što nije u redu?

174
00:23:03,473 --> 00:23:04,553
Ubaci je unutra!

175
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:50,220
Nema primjedbi
na samuraja?

176
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:53,220
Požuri.
Prije nego stigne do grada

177
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,740
Što je bilo?

178
00:25:20,729 --> 00:25:21,689
Zovem se Katsushiro Okamoto.

179
00:25:21,889 --> 00:25:24,329
Ucini me svojim ucenikom!

180
00:25:26,529 --> 00:25:27,529
Ucenikom?

181
00:25:28,645 --> 00:25:31,965
Zovem se Kimbei Shimada.
Ja sam ronin.

182
00:25:33,125 --> 00:25:35,205
I ne uzimam ucenike.

183
00:25:35,685 --> 00:25:38,045
Ustani. Razgovarat cemo.

184
00:25:38,925 --> 00:25:41,085
Molim te ! Uzmi me kao svojeg ucenika!

185
00:25:41,765 --> 00:25:45,565
Ustani! Pricat cemo dok hodamo

186
00:25:59,207 --> 00:26:01,167
Sramotiš me

187
00:26:01,367 --> 00:26:03,887
Precjenjuješ me

188
00:26:05,407 --> 00:26:06,407
Slušaj

189
00:26:07,207 --> 00:26:09,927
Ja ne posjedujem nikakve
specijalne vještine!

190
00:26:10,887 --> 00:26:13,287
Ali imam puno iskustva iz bitki,

191
00:26:14,087 --> 00:26:16,327
Gubeci bitke, sve

192
00:26:16,727 --> 00:26:19,367
Ukratko, ja sam takav.

193
00:26:19,847 --> 00:26:22,287
Okani se te zamisli za
vlastito dobro.

194
00:26:22,807 --> 00:26:25,207
Ne, gospodine.
Odlucio sam!

195
00:26:26,831 --> 00:26:29,031
Ja cu vas pratiti, gospodine.

196
00:26:29,271 --> 00:26:30,391
Zabranjujem ti.

197
00:26:31,391 --> 00:26:33,951
Ne mogu dozvoliti sebi da vucem
dijete za sobom.

198
00:26:46,311 --> 00:26:47,791
Što želite?

199
00:26:55,751 --> 00:26:57,031
Što ti želiš?

200
00:27:05,551 --> 00:27:06,711
Bezobrazan si!

201
00:27:08,151 --> 00:27:09,991
Dijete, gledaj svoja posla!

202
00:27:14,729 --> 00:27:16,649
Da li ste vi samuraj?

203
00:27:20,969 --> 00:27:22,169
Naravno!

204
00:27:25,249 --> 00:27:26,129
Pitam se

205
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:53,919
Tko je on?

206
00:28:00,239 --> 00:28:01,599
Ne obracaj pažnju.

207
00:28:20,387 --> 00:28:22,227
Molim vas, gospodine! Bojim se pitati!

208
00:28:25,067 --> 00:28:26,467
Zašto ne poðeš kuci?

209
00:28:28,867 --> 00:28:32,627
Zar ti nije bilo dosta?
Kada se najede sam ce otici.

210
00:28:37,987 --> 00:28:39,227
To je nemoguce.

211
00:28:40,027 --> 00:28:40,987
Gospodine!

212
00:28:41,787 --> 00:28:44,067
Zašto ih ne naoružate sa...?

213
00:28:44,267 --> 00:28:45,507
Pomislio sam i na to.

214
00:28:45,667 --> 00:28:46,787
Ali gospodine

215
00:28:50,932 --> 00:28:52,692
To ne bi bila igra.

216
00:28:56,492 --> 00:28:58,012
Grupa od cetrdeset razbojnika!

217
00:28:59,052 --> 00:29:02,052
Dva ili tri samuraja ne bi
ništa postigli.

218
00:29:17,102 --> 00:29:19,462
Obrana je teža nego napad.

219
00:29:22,022 --> 00:29:23,662
Planine iza sela?

220
00:29:25,022 --> 00:29:26,502
Mogu li ih konji preci?

221
00:29:36,542 --> 00:29:38,222
Polja sa prednje strane.

222
00:29:40,028 --> 00:29:42,308
Selo je potpuno dostupno
konjanicima...

223
00:29:42,908 --> 00:29:45,108
dok se polja ne poplave

224
00:29:47,068 --> 00:29:50,148
Potrebno je cetiri stražara.
Svaki da pazi na jednu stranu.

225
00:29:51,548 --> 00:29:53,308
Još dva kao rezerva.

226
00:29:56,021 --> 00:30:01,581
Trebat ce vam još najmanje sedmorica,
ukljucujuci i mene.

227
00:30:03,861 --> 00:30:05,901
Možemo li si priuštiti sedmoro, a?

228
00:30:06,341 --> 00:30:08,621
Djeda je rekao "cetvoro,"
zar ne?

229
00:30:08,861 --> 00:30:10,541
Ali još trojica.

230
00:30:11,461 --> 00:30:12,221
Cekaj!

231
00:30:12,941 --> 00:30:14,461
Nisam rekao "Pristajem!"

232
00:30:14,861 --> 00:30:16,221
Samo razmišljam.

233
00:30:18,461 --> 00:30:22,541
Kao prvo, nije lako pronaci
sedam pouzdanih samuraja.

234
00:30:23,381 --> 00:30:28,061
Pogotovo kada je nagrada za trud
tri bijedna obroka.

235
00:30:30,061 --> 00:30:31,741
I ako mogu reci da je to smiješno.

236
00:30:33,943 --> 00:30:35,103
Osim toga...

237
00:30:36,223 --> 00:30:38,303
Dosta mi je borbe.

238
00:30:39,863 --> 00:30:40,743
Možda mi je vrijeme.

239
00:31:02,728 --> 00:31:04,848
Drago mi je što nisam
roðen kao farmer!

240
00:31:07,048 --> 00:31:08,048
I pas ima više srece!

241
00:31:08,848 --> 00:31:12,488
Sranje! Vjerujte mi!
Idite i objesite se!

242
00:31:14,568 --> 00:31:15,488
Zaveži!

243
00:31:16,168 --> 00:31:18,048
Što? Ja vam govorim onako kako je!

244
00:31:19,935 --> 00:31:20,775
Onako kako je?

245
00:31:21,735 --> 00:31:23,615
Zar ih ni malo
ne sažalijevaš?

246
00:31:24,095 --> 00:31:25,175
Nemoj me nasmijavati!

247
00:31:26,175 --> 00:31:27,255
Imaš li sažaljenja?

248
00:31:29,135 --> 00:31:31,415
Ako imaš, zašto
im ne pomogneš?

249
00:31:38,080 --> 00:31:38,840
Hoceš se tuci?

250
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:42,960
Prestani!

251
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:49,800
Prestani!

252
00:31:58,591 --> 00:31:59,351
Hej! Samuraju!

253
00:32:00,431 --> 00:32:03,031
Vidi ovo!
Ovo je za tebe!

254
00:32:03,551 --> 00:32:07,711
Znaš li što te budale jedu?
Proso!

255
00:32:08,431 --> 00:32:11,711
Hrane te rižom,
a žive na prosu.

256
00:32:12,688 --> 00:32:15,648
Trude se!

257
00:32:18,208 --> 00:32:19,528
Vidim.

258
00:32:21,343 --> 00:32:22,103
Ne moraš ništa više reci!

259
00:32:26,704 --> 00:32:29,664
Necu trošiti vašu hranu.

260
00:32:42,508 --> 00:32:49,188
Gledaj!
Manzovi dolaze kuci!

261
00:33:02,788 --> 00:33:03,948
Gdje su Rikichi i Yohei?

262
00:33:04,588 --> 00:33:06,668
Još uvijek traže samuraja!

263
00:33:06,828 --> 00:33:08,468
Zar zaista misliš da
ce samuraj doci?

264
00:33:08,628 --> 00:33:09,948
Da, dolaze. Sedmorica.

265
00:33:10,108 --> 00:33:11,468
Da, sedam.

266
00:33:16,289 --> 00:33:19,129
Hm... sedam!

267
00:33:20,089 --> 00:33:23,369
Rekao si "cetiri", pa sam se usprotivio.

268
00:33:25,249 --> 00:33:30,089
Mislio sam da cemo
morati unajmiti desetoricu.

269
00:33:30,369 --> 00:33:35,409
Ali, da sam ti to rekao,
ti bi doveo petnaestoricu

270
00:33:35,929 --> 00:33:38,849
Vidiš na što sam mislio?

271
00:33:39,889 --> 00:33:43,289
Djede! Zabrinut sam!

272
00:33:47,529 --> 00:33:50,689
Naše djevojke su lude
za samurajima.

273
00:33:51,129 --> 00:33:54,449
Seljanima nece biti drago da ih
vide sa njima

274
00:33:59,363 --> 00:34:02,123
Budalo! Zar si zaboravio
na razbojnike?

275
00:34:03,083 --> 00:34:06,443
Zašto brineš za bradu,

276
00:34:06,603 --> 00:34:08,403
kada ce ti skinuti glavu?

277
00:34:31,803 --> 00:34:33,363
Treba li ti moja pomoc?

278
00:34:34,763 --> 00:34:35,923
Protiv koga se boriti?

279
00:34:38,875 --> 00:34:39,915
Katsuishiro!

280
00:34:52,275 --> 00:34:54,035
Drži svoje oružje cvrsto.

281
00:34:56,235 --> 00:34:58,435
Udari ga cim doðe

282
00:35:10,532 --> 00:35:12,332
Udari što jace možeš!

283
00:35:42,508 --> 00:35:43,428
Divno!

284
00:35:45,148 --> 00:35:46,508
Molimo vas da nam oprostite

285
00:35:47,028 --> 00:35:48,948
Zovem se Kambei Shimada

286
00:35:49,148 --> 00:35:53,028
Trebaju mi talentirani ljudi,
odmah

287
00:35:53,388 --> 00:35:54,948
Oprostite nam

288
00:35:55,308 --> 00:35:56,828
Što je ovo?

289
00:35:57,228 --> 00:35:59,468
Nedopustivo! Necuveno!

290
00:35:59,668 --> 00:36:02,228
Oprostite mi. Vidite,

291
00:36:02,428 --> 00:36:06,668
sprema se rat protiv
bande razbojnika

292
00:36:09,111 --> 00:36:12,151
Koji Klan?

293
00:36:12,231 --> 00:36:15,031
Naš poslodavac je,
kako da kažem,

294
00:36:15,191 --> 00:36:17,791
farmersko selo.

295
00:36:19,887 --> 00:36:23,167
Posao nam ne garantira ni placu ni nagradu,

296
00:36:23,647 --> 00:36:27,087
nego tri obroka dok smo na dužnosti.

297
00:36:27,247 --> 00:36:28,607
Koja glupost!

298
00:36:29,527 --> 00:36:31,607
Moja ambicija je malo veca.

299
00:36:33,127 --> 00:36:34,527
Žao mi je.

300
00:36:35,807 --> 00:36:37,487
Je li to tvoja zadnja rijec?

301
00:36:38,127 --> 00:36:39,047
Da!

302
00:36:48,023 --> 00:36:50,783
Veliki gubitak, gospodine!

303
00:37:37,383 --> 00:37:38,663
Što je bilo?

304
00:37:39,143 --> 00:37:43,423
Samuraj je dobar.
Ali sam zabrinut za ostalu šestoricu.

305
00:37:44,441 --> 00:37:46,201
Ne luduj!

306
00:37:46,441 --> 00:37:50,161
Prvo ih provjeri.
Pa onda budi zabrinut!

307
00:38:06,680 --> 00:38:07,800
Isprobaj ga!

308
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:27,920
Samo trenutak, gospodine!

309
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:31,760
Kao prošli put?

310
00:38:36,865 --> 00:38:39,505
Da. Radi tvojeg treninga.

311
00:39:11,720 --> 00:39:13,120
Molim vas! Bez šala.

312
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:15,760
Oprostite mi.

313
00:39:31,377 --> 00:39:32,577
Interesantno.

314
00:39:35,417 --> 00:39:36,777
Ali...

315
00:39:38,057 --> 00:39:40,377
Shvacam da farmeri pate

316
00:39:41,017 --> 00:39:44,857
Mislim da razumijem zašto
ste prihvatili

317
00:39:45,257 --> 00:39:49,537
Prihvatit cu samo zato
što me fasciniraš.

318
00:39:51,097 --> 00:39:55,257
I najvece prijateljstvo se raða
iz slucajnog susreta.

319
00:40:02,583 --> 00:40:03,823
Kako se zoveš?

320
00:40:04,103 --> 00:40:05,623
Gorobei Katayama

321
00:40:05,823 --> 00:40:07,183
Zvuci jako, ali...

322
00:40:17,943 --> 00:40:20,463
Yohei, što nije u redu!
Požuri!

323
00:40:25,503 --> 00:40:26,823
Hajde!

324
00:40:31,472 --> 00:40:32,432
Yohei, što nije u redu?

325
00:40:34,272 --> 00:40:36,192
Riža je nestala!

326
00:40:48,032 --> 00:40:49,112
Budalo!

327
00:40:49,272 --> 00:40:50,832
Pa rekao sam vam...

328
00:40:51,552 --> 00:40:53,712
Dao sam sve od sebe da je sacuvam!

329
00:40:59,641 --> 00:41:03,441
Nocu sam spavao pored nje!

330
00:41:08,601 --> 00:41:10,361
Donijet cu malo od kuce!

331
00:41:11,441 --> 00:41:14,921
Ali što cemo dok se ne vratiš?

332
00:41:15,921 --> 00:41:19,881
Sve je odneseno,
osim šacice

333
00:42:12,897 --> 00:42:14,417
Ne budite smiješni!

334
00:42:14,937 --> 00:42:16,777
Stiže!

335
00:42:23,712 --> 00:42:26,032
Ovo je velicanstveno!
Hvala nebesima!

336
00:42:29,032 --> 00:42:31,152
Lijepo je vidjeti vas žive!

337
00:42:31,352 --> 00:42:34,432
Vec sam se oprostio od tebe!

338
00:42:41,472 --> 00:42:43,472
Kako si pobjegao?

339
00:42:45,041 --> 00:42:48,401
Ležao sam u jarku,
ispod biljaka

340
00:42:50,921 --> 00:42:54,441
Kada je dvorac dogorio,
i pao na mene,

341
00:42:54,641 --> 00:42:56,561
Mislio sam da sam gotov!

342
00:42:57,641 --> 00:42:59,361
Da li si se bojao?

343
00:43:00,761 --> 00:43:03,321
Ne narocito.

344
00:43:05,761 --> 00:43:08,081
Da li ti je dosta borbe?

345
00:43:18,120 --> 00:43:18,880
Naprotiv,

346
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:21,280
Upravo se spremam za težak rat.

347
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:25,280
Nece nam donijeti slavu ili novac.
Hoceš li nam se pridružiti?

348
00:43:25,480 --> 00:43:26,640
Da!

349
00:43:27,560 --> 00:43:29,000
Možda ovog puta poginemo.

350
00:43:50,549 --> 00:43:52,309
Nisam znao da su u tako malom broju.

351
00:43:52,629 --> 00:43:54,629
Što tražite, gospodine?

352
00:43:54,749 --> 00:43:57,669
Samuraja.

353
00:43:58,949 --> 00:44:02,709
Imam jednog u dvorištu,
ali je loše kvalitete.

354
00:43:59,679 --> 00:44:03,239
Zapanjila me je njegova
sretna nezainteresiranost.

355
00:44:04,127 --> 00:44:06,487
Ušao je rekavši:
"Nahrani me. Nemam novca,

356
00:44:06,647 --> 00:44:09,127
Ali cu ti isjeci drva za vatru."

357
00:44:19,917 --> 00:44:22,397
Dopala mi se njegova otvorenost

358
00:45:02,933 --> 00:45:05,853
Zar nikada nisi vidio kako se cjepaju
drva za vatru?

359
00:45:06,053 --> 00:45:08,253
Izgledaš kao da uživaš u tome.

360
00:45:09,013 --> 00:45:11,733
O, to mi je u krvi

361
00:45:16,933 --> 00:45:18,173
Dobar si u tome

362
00:45:19,797 --> 00:45:21,637
Ali sam ja bolji u
ubijanju neprijatelja

363
00:45:22,277 --> 00:45:23,517
Mnogo si ih ubio?

364
00:45:23,997 --> 00:45:27,477
Pa - nemoguce je
ubiti ih sve.

365
00:45:32,436 --> 00:45:34,676
Tako da ja obicno pobjegnem.

366
00:45:37,156 --> 00:45:39,076
Fantastican nacin rada!

367
00:45:40,516 --> 00:45:41,676
Hvala.

368
00:45:48,821 --> 00:45:50,781
Usput,

369
00:45:50,941 --> 00:45:54,021
Da li si zainteresiran da
ubiješ trideset razbojnika?

370
00:46:12,450 --> 00:46:13,450
Pocnimo

371
00:47:45,335 --> 00:47:47,375
Šteta. Izjednaceno.

372
00:47:48,095 --> 00:47:49,095
Ne,

373
00:47:49,935 --> 00:47:51,095
Ja sam pobijedio

374
00:47:54,865 --> 00:47:55,905
Jesi?

375
00:47:57,785 --> 00:47:59,785
Da smo se stvarno borili,
bio bi proboden i mrtav.

376
00:48:05,465 --> 00:48:06,385
Da vidimo!

377
00:48:06,785 --> 00:48:07,785
Nema potrebe.

378
00:48:08,145 --> 00:48:09,305
Zar ne vidiš?

379
00:48:09,625 --> 00:48:12,185
Pravi mac bi te ubio.
Nema koristi.

380
00:48:14,048 --> 00:48:15,128
Cekaj!

381
00:48:20,328 --> 00:48:22,528
Stani! Možeš ti pricati što hoceš.

382
00:49:01,319 --> 00:49:02,559
Kakva šteta.

383
00:49:03,959 --> 00:49:05,519
Tako je ocito

384
00:49:38,227 --> 00:49:39,547
Jesi našao nekog?

385
00:49:43,387 --> 00:49:44,827
Promašio sam jednog

386
00:49:45,027 --> 00:49:47,427
Prvoklasni macevalac

387
00:49:47,947 --> 00:49:49,667
Izgubljena riba izgleda velika

388
00:49:50,107 --> 00:49:55,507
Ali sam vidio njegovu hrabrost
svojim ocima.

389
00:50:03,607 --> 00:50:04,767
Fantastican je!

390
00:50:05,087 --> 00:50:08,847
Covjek koji je zainteresiran u usavršavanje
svojih sposobnosti.

391
00:50:09,527 --> 00:50:11,367
Tako da je njegovo odgovor bio "Ne!"

392
00:50:11,687 --> 00:50:13,647
Šteta!

393
00:50:16,081 --> 00:50:18,281
Ali sam mu ipak rekao
gdje me može naci

394
00:50:18,961 --> 00:50:20,361
A ti?

395
00:50:21,321 --> 00:50:22,561
Uhvatio sam jednog.

396
00:50:23,561 --> 00:50:26,041
Njegovo macevanje je... nije baš najbolje

397
00:50:28,602 --> 00:50:30,842
Ali je pravi lik.

398
00:50:31,762 --> 00:50:33,522
Veseo momak.

399
00:50:34,562 --> 00:50:36,482
Dobro društvo u borbi

400
00:50:38,002 --> 00:50:38,922
Puno hvala

401
00:50:40,962 --> 00:50:44,082
I ja sam uhvatio jednog.

402
00:50:44,322 --> 00:50:46,442
Onaj obucen kao prosjak?

403
00:50:46,802 --> 00:50:49,442
Da. Bio mi je desna
ruka godinama.

404
00:50:56,329 --> 00:50:57,569
Donijet cu cistu vodu.

405
00:51:02,129 --> 00:51:06,169
Ja sam Heinachi Hayashida, macevalac
iz Wood Cut Škole.

406
00:51:12,729 --> 00:51:15,249
Dobro, još trojicu da naðemo.

407
00:51:15,529 --> 00:51:16,489
Trojicu?

408
00:51:16,769 --> 00:51:18,049
Dvojicu

409
00:51:18,329 --> 00:51:19,849
Ne možemo povesti Dijete.

410
00:51:22,334 --> 00:51:23,134
Gospodine.

411
00:51:23,534 --> 00:51:24,694
Znam.

412
00:51:25,614 --> 00:51:27,574
Znam Što ce te reci.

413
00:51:28,294 --> 00:51:31,254
I ja sam nekada bio mladic kao ti.

414
00:51:34,135 --> 00:51:36,015
"Sam treniraj

415
00:51:36,375 --> 00:51:39,415
"Istici se u ratu

416
00:51:40,815 --> 00:51:43,975
"Jer bi jednom mogao,
biti gospodar rata!"

417
00:51:44,495 --> 00:51:47,055
Ali vrijeme leti.

418
00:51:47,855 --> 00:51:51,375
Osjedit ceš prije nego što tvoj san postane
stvarnost

419
00:51:53,855 --> 00:51:55,255
Do tada,

420
00:51:56,095 --> 00:52:00,455
tvoji roditelji i prijatelji
su mrtvi

421
00:52:49,798 --> 00:52:52,678
Vrati se kuci,
kreni ujutro

422
00:52:52,878 --> 00:52:54,638
imao si dovoljno treninga zadnjih
par dana

423
00:52:55,278 --> 00:52:56,598
Dobro iskustvo

424
00:53:12,815 --> 00:53:13,735
Molim vas, gospodine!

425
00:53:13,895 --> 00:53:15,415
Svakako ga povedite.
Molim vas!

426
00:53:15,655 --> 00:53:16,535
Ali...

427
00:53:17,095 --> 00:53:20,495
Uradi tako! Iako ga zovete
djetetom

428
00:53:21,095 --> 00:53:23,135
Djeca su cesto više voljna
nego odrasli

429
00:53:24,495 --> 00:53:27,295
Imajuci na umu da bismo ga tretirali
kao odraslog

430
00:53:28,415 --> 00:53:31,055
Pa, tretirajmo ga kao odraslog

431
00:53:38,070 --> 00:53:39,470
Još dvoje

432
00:53:40,510 --> 00:53:43,630
Mislim da treba još jedan

433
00:53:45,910 --> 00:53:46,830
Zdravo!

434
00:53:49,830 --> 00:53:51,230
Došao si!

435
00:53:52,870 --> 00:53:54,070
Hvala

436
00:53:55,110 --> 00:53:57,230
-I...?
-Krecemo sutra

437
00:54:01,453 --> 00:54:02,293
Sutra?

438
00:54:04,173 --> 00:54:07,093
Zaboravimo na sedmog.
Nemamo vremena za gubljenje!

439
00:54:10,773 --> 00:54:11,853
Pa

440
00:54:15,133 --> 00:54:16,333
Gospodine!

441
00:54:17,653 --> 00:54:19,253
-Gospodine!
-U redu je

442
00:54:21,583 --> 00:54:24,703
-Gospodine!
-Znam.

443
00:54:29,383 --> 00:54:32,063
Hej! Našao sam samuraja!

444
00:54:32,223 --> 00:54:33,703
Stvarno jakog!

445
00:54:34,383 --> 00:54:37,263
Nemilosrdnog!
On je kao divlji pas

446
00:54:37,423 --> 00:54:40,383
Pio je kasnije sa njim

447
00:54:40,583 --> 00:54:43,103
Pitao sam ga. Stiže!

448
00:54:46,183 --> 00:54:47,423
Da li da...?

449
00:55:03,437 --> 00:55:04,797
Što to radiš?

450
00:55:05,357 --> 00:55:06,517
Testiram

451
00:55:08,877 --> 00:55:10,677
Nije fer!

452
00:55:10,917 --> 00:55:11,997
Samo gledaj

453
00:55:12,397 --> 00:55:14,157
Dobar samuraj ce izbjeci.

454
00:55:14,317 --> 00:55:16,437
Ali, on je pijan

455
00:55:16,597 --> 00:55:18,997
Pravi samuraj se nikada nece toliko napiti

456
00:55:23,997 --> 00:55:24,997
Evo me!

457
00:55:33,517 --> 00:55:35,117
Vidiš, rekao sam ti!

458
00:56:09,316 --> 00:56:11,116
Tko me je udario?

459
00:56:53,180 --> 00:56:54,140
O! To si ti

460
00:56:57,780 --> 00:57:00,300
Sjecam se tvoje glave!
Vidim je cak i u snovima!

461
00:57:03,180 --> 00:57:10,740
Usudio si se pitati me jesam li ja samuraj!

462
00:57:20,259 --> 00:57:25,339
Gledaj! Iako sam u ragama,
Ja sam pravi samuraj!

463
00:57:29,419 --> 00:57:33,259
Cijelo vrijeme sam te tražio!

464
00:57:34,819 --> 00:57:36,619
Htio sam ti pokazati ovo!

465
00:57:44,899 --> 00:57:45,619
Vidi ovo!

466
00:57:46,579 --> 00:57:51,499
Samo da znaš... nekada je
pripadalo uglednoj samurajskoj porodici

467
00:58:11,994 --> 00:58:13,194
Ovo sam ja!

468
00:58:15,234 --> 00:58:17,394
Kikuchiyo? Je li ti to ime?

469
00:58:17,754 --> 00:58:18,994
Da, gospodine!

470
00:58:20,154 --> 00:58:22,994
"Roðen sedamnaestog veljace,
druga godina Tenshoa"

471
00:58:25,994 --> 00:58:26,994
Što je tako smiješno?

472
00:58:28,874 --> 00:58:30,794
Ne izgledaš kao da ti je trinaest!

473
00:58:32,794 --> 00:58:36,034
Slušaj! Ako si ti Kikuchiyo
koji se ovdje spominje

474
00:58:36,434 --> 00:58:38,354
ti bi morao imati trinaest godina

475
00:58:44,826 --> 00:58:46,546
Gdje si ukrao ovo?

476
00:58:48,266 --> 00:58:49,306
Ukrao?

477
00:58:57,466 --> 00:58:58,466
Dovraga samuraju!

478
00:59:02,226 --> 00:59:02,866
Prokletstvo!

479
00:59:23,057 --> 00:59:24,337
Miran budi, trinaestogodišnjak!

480
01:00:09,593 --> 01:00:10,513
Gospodine Kikuchiyo!

481
01:00:15,913 --> 01:00:17,473
Hrabrost, trinaestogodišnjaku!

482
01:00:27,818 --> 01:00:29,658
Dovraga sa samurajima!

483
01:00:46,298 --> 01:00:47,778
Je li on stvarno samuraj?

484
01:00:47,978 --> 01:00:49,778
On misli da je

485
01:01:13,251 --> 01:01:14,331
"Dobro pazi na ovo!"

486
01:01:17,091 --> 01:01:18,291
Povedi me sa sobom!

487
01:02:00,790 --> 01:02:02,070
Tata, Što nije u redu?

488
01:02:19,701 --> 01:02:23,301
Zašto me tako gledaš?

489
01:02:32,341 --> 01:02:35,181
Shino! Ošišaj se!

490
01:02:35,821 --> 01:02:38,181
Ošišaj se! Obuci se kao djecak!

491
01:02:41,410 --> 01:02:42,170
Ne razumijem!

492
01:02:42,610 --> 01:02:45,730
Ošišaj, kad ti kažem!
Kažem ti to zato što te volim!

493
01:02:45,930 --> 01:02:49,450
Samuraji dolaze! Ne znaš
što ce ti napraviti

494
01:02:49,610 --> 01:02:51,530
-Hajde, ošišaj se.
-Ne, necu

495
01:03:24,232 --> 01:03:27,752
Ali Manzovi su vidjeli te samuraje!

496
01:03:28,592 --> 01:03:30,552
I on je odrezao njenu kosu!

497
01:03:30,952 --> 01:03:34,032
Vi niste zabrinuti zato
što ste djecaci, ali...

498
01:03:34,272 --> 01:03:37,312
-Ja cu.
-Ti zadrži moju kcerku.

499
01:03:37,472 --> 01:03:39,792
Bit ce sigurnija kod tebe

500
01:03:40,938 --> 01:03:43,498
Budalo!
Govorim o Manzou!

501
01:03:43,978 --> 01:03:46,698
Kaže da je zabrinut za
naše selo!

502
01:03:47,058 --> 01:03:50,458
Ali on je samo zabrinut
za svoju kcerku! Dovraga!

503
01:04:10,746 --> 01:04:12,306
Ti si budala!

504
01:04:13,226 --> 01:04:17,266
Svi koji imaju kcerke su
preplašeni

505
01:04:19,146 --> 01:04:20,906
Što da ucinimo?

506
01:04:21,506 --> 01:04:23,586
Samuraji stižu jednog od narednih dana!

507
01:04:25,764 --> 01:04:28,204
Hajdemo! Idemo do Djeda!

508
01:04:30,604 --> 01:04:32,804
Ne stoj! Idemo!

509
01:04:34,924 --> 01:04:36,444
Pokret!

510
01:04:37,804 --> 01:04:41,364
Trebali bi nešto uciniti
prije nego što samuraji stignu!

511
01:04:48,770 --> 01:04:50,050
Još nas prati!

512
01:06:35,707 --> 01:06:37,707
Ne vidim ga!

513
01:06:38,667 --> 01:06:40,067
Odustao?

514
01:06:40,667 --> 01:06:44,427
Cudno, zar ne?
Sada mi, nekako...

515
01:06:44,867 --> 01:06:46,587
nedostaje!

516
01:06:53,019 --> 01:06:54,099
Ovuda!

517
01:06:57,219 --> 01:06:58,499
Sheeyit!

518
01:07:12,147 --> 01:07:13,867
Znaci to je naš dvorac, a?

519
01:07:14,987 --> 01:07:17,467
Ha! S druge strane
ne bih htio da umrem u gomili balege

520
01:07:17,707 --> 01:07:19,947
Nismo rekli da bi ti trebao

521
01:07:39,295 --> 01:07:41,215
Stigli smo!

522
01:07:41,375 --> 01:07:43,095
Doveo sam samuraje!

523
01:07:54,415 --> 01:07:55,935
Što nije u redu?

524
01:07:56,095 --> 01:07:57,655
Stižu samuraji!

525
01:08:04,888 --> 01:08:06,208
Molim!

526
01:08:10,768 --> 01:08:12,248
Što nije u redu?

527
01:08:26,776 --> 01:08:28,736
Pa kakvo je ovo
gostoprimstvo?

528
01:08:32,336 --> 01:08:34,216
Što ovo znaci?

529
01:08:37,016 --> 01:08:40,936
Hej! Što je bilo?
Poželite dobrodošlicu vašim gostima!

530
01:08:57,713 --> 01:08:59,513
Idemo do Djeda

531
01:08:59,673 --> 01:09:03,273
On brine o svemu

532
01:09:03,473 --> 01:09:04,793
Seoski patrijarh, a?

533
01:09:06,593 --> 01:09:08,633
Primit ce nas

534
01:09:09,073 --> 01:09:10,553
Kakva cast!

535
01:09:14,673 --> 01:09:16,033
Idemo

536
01:10:29,209 --> 01:10:34,169
Zaista su budalasti

537
01:10:34,849 --> 01:10:40,649
Farmeri uvijek brinu, te za ovo,
te za ono

538
01:10:41,049 --> 01:10:44,889
Kiše, suša, vjetrovi

539
01:10:46,769 --> 01:10:50,809
Drugacije receno, probude se ujutro
zabrinuti i na isti nacin odu u krevet

540
01:10:50,969 --> 01:10:52,889
Današnji dan nije izuzetak

541
01:10:53,569 --> 01:10:59,089
Samo su uplašeni,
uplašeni bez razloga

542
01:11:01,717 --> 01:11:03,117
Ali slušaj

543
01:11:03,797 --> 01:11:06,477
Zašto se plaše nas?

544
01:11:07,517 --> 01:11:10,957
A u isto vrijeme ocekuju da
ucinimo nešto za njih?

545
01:11:20,614 --> 01:11:21,334
Razbojnici!

546
01:11:45,286 --> 01:11:47,566
Molim vas! Samuraji, Molim vas!

547
01:11:57,559 --> 01:11:59,399
Pomozite! Razbojnici dolaze!

548
01:12:01,009 --> 01:12:02,329
Molimo vas pomozite!

549
01:10:43,223 --> 01:10:44,143
Budite mirni!

550
01:12:04,167 --> 01:12:04,967
Smirite se!

551
01:12:08,363 --> 01:12:10,203
Odgovori mi razgovijetno!

552
01:12:11,083 --> 01:12:13,483
Iz kojeg pravca dolaze?

553
01:12:17,199 --> 01:12:18,679
Iz planina!

554
01:12:19,959 --> 01:12:21,239
Sa prednjeg puta!

555
01:12:22,879 --> 01:12:25,039
Oni koji su vidjeli razbojnike,
neka naprave korak naprijed!

556
01:12:27,264 --> 01:12:29,424
Tko je vidio razbojnike?

557
01:12:30,272 --> 01:12:31,872
Tko je oglasio uzbunu?

558
01:12:32,320 --> 01:12:33,360
Ja sam!

559
01:12:50,512 --> 01:12:51,832
Ne morate se bojati!

560
01:12:52,193 --> 01:12:54,593
Nema razbojnika!

561
01:12:59,192 --> 01:13:00,192
Budale!

562
01:13:00,672 --> 01:13:04,472
Docekali ste nas kao što
biste docekali kugu!

563
01:13:04,872 --> 01:13:06,952
ali kada ste culi alarm...

564
01:13:07,112 --> 01:13:09,232
O! Samuraji!

565
01:13:11,712 --> 01:13:13,792
Poceli ste nas obožavati

566
01:13:18,792 --> 01:13:20,272
Budale!

567
01:13:39,193 --> 01:13:41,113
Djede, imaš li kakvih primjedbi?

568
01:13:41,513 --> 01:13:42,873
Ne

569
01:13:43,513 --> 01:13:44,633
Sve je u redu sada

570
01:13:50,793 --> 01:13:53,273
Pa, izgleda da je on ipak od neke koristi

571
01:13:53,673 --> 01:13:54,873
Sada nas je sedmorica, a?

572
01:14:04,536 --> 01:14:06,336
Ispricavamo se što je ovdje ovako prljavo

573
01:14:06,856 --> 01:14:09,136
Ali gdje cete živjeti?

574
01:14:10,376 --> 01:14:12,016
Ja cu spavati u staji

575
01:14:12,176 --> 01:14:13,336
Sa konjima?

576
01:14:14,616 --> 01:14:17,176
Nema konja! Razbojnici su ih odveli prošle godine

577
01:14:35,769 --> 01:14:38,969
Staja je fino mjesto za spavanje sa ženom

578
01:14:43,289 --> 01:14:44,849
Nemam ženu!

579
01:14:59,081 --> 01:15:00,161
Budalo!

580
01:15:14,064 --> 01:15:15,624
Kako se stvarno zoveš?

581
01:15:18,824 --> 01:15:20,264
Ne sjecam se

582
01:15:21,024 --> 01:15:22,904
Daj mi neko dobro ime

583
01:15:23,704 --> 01:15:25,424
Kikuchiyo!

584
01:15:26,944 --> 01:15:28,504
Dobro ti stoji

585
01:15:49,814 --> 01:15:52,254
Kako bi ti napao ovo selo?

586
01:15:52,774 --> 01:15:54,614
Jurišao bih sa planine

587
01:15:56,694 --> 01:15:59,054
Niz ovaj put?
I ja bih isto ucinio

588
01:15:59,734 --> 01:16:01,974
Zapad

589
01:16:16,878 --> 01:16:18,838
Kako bi obranio?

590
01:16:19,318 --> 01:16:20,918
Shichiroji dobro zna svoj posao

591
01:16:21,918 --> 01:16:23,198
Pogledaj ona debla

592
01:16:23,958 --> 01:16:25,398
Hoce postaviti ogradu

593
01:16:26,238 --> 01:16:27,558
Tvoja stara desna ruka, a?

594
01:16:57,876 --> 01:16:59,276
Zapamtite!

595
01:17:00,476 --> 01:17:01,836
Rat je juriš

596
01:17:02,393 --> 01:17:04,713
Jurišamo i kada smo u obrani i u napadu

597
01:17:05,343 --> 01:17:07,863
A kada nemaš gdje jurišati,
onda je vrijeme za umrijeti

598
01:17:29,367 --> 01:17:31,527
Jug

599
01:17:44,762 --> 01:17:47,722
Posle žetve cemo poplaviti tu oblast

600
01:17:48,402 --> 01:17:50,682
Onda ce ta strana biti dobro zašticena

601
01:17:51,362 --> 01:17:53,682
Da li cemo imati dovoljno vremena da to napravimo?

602
01:18:02,749 --> 01:18:06,589
Koplje! Kreni naprijed sa kopljem!

603
01:18:07,189 --> 01:18:09,029
Gledaj! Ja sam razbojnik!

604
01:18:16,851 --> 01:18:18,091
Hajde!

605
01:18:27,521 --> 01:18:28,441
Sljedeci!

606
01:18:59,057 --> 01:19:01,657
Istok

607
01:19:05,515 --> 01:19:07,155
Uništit cemo ovaj most

608
01:19:07,555 --> 01:19:09,315
Onda ce ova granica biti sigurna

609
01:19:16,835 --> 01:19:18,995
Što je sa onim kucama?

610
01:19:27,361 --> 01:19:29,401
Morat cemo ih evakuirati

611
01:19:34,121 --> 01:19:35,481
Mlin takoðer?

612
01:19:38,081 --> 01:19:40,841
Taj starac je tvrdoglav

613
01:19:47,081 --> 01:19:48,361
Zapamti

614
01:19:48,641 --> 01:19:51,401
Vi se bojite neprijatelja

615
01:19:53,074 --> 01:19:56,234
Ali se, takoðer, oni boje i vas

616
01:20:26,066 --> 01:20:27,506
Divan si!

617
01:20:28,706 --> 01:20:30,706
Divna strašila!

618
01:20:33,618 --> 01:20:36,778
Ali to su ljudi, a ne vrapci ili vrane!

619
01:20:46,139 --> 01:20:48,459
Ti, što žvaceš!

620
01:20:48,619 --> 01:20:49,899
Prestani!

621
01:20:53,755 --> 01:20:55,275
Nisi krava!

622
01:21:06,515 --> 01:21:09,115
Ti na kraju! Istupi!

623
01:21:11,755 --> 01:21:13,235
Na tebe mislim!

624
01:21:13,995 --> 01:21:15,235
Ti!

625
01:21:35,635 --> 01:21:37,595
Ako želiš gledati, plati ulaznicu

626
01:21:57,414 --> 01:21:58,654
Što je ovo?

627
01:22:00,272 --> 01:22:02,032
Koplje, gospodine

628
01:22:03,648 --> 01:22:05,688
Gdje si ga našao?

629
01:22:07,048 --> 01:22:08,728
Raste iz grmlja?

630
01:22:11,768 --> 01:22:12,888
Znam!

631
01:22:13,408 --> 01:22:14,968
Samuraj u begu!

632
01:22:15,848 --> 01:22:19,008
Ako imaš jedno, i ostali ih
sigurno imaju

633
01:22:20,528 --> 01:22:21,608
Imaš li?

634
01:22:22,168 --> 01:22:23,648
Da-li-imate-koplja?

635
01:22:32,928 --> 01:22:35,928
Sjever

636
01:22:45,180 --> 01:22:49,140
Izgleda mirno.
Ali je u stvari nesigurno

637
01:23:25,430 --> 01:23:27,630
Katsushiro!
Odlazimo!

638
01:23:27,790 --> 01:23:28,630
Da, gospodine! Stižem!

639
01:23:37,030 --> 01:23:38,230
Još uvijek Dijete

640
01:24:41,070 --> 01:24:43,310
Jesi li ti jedan od seljana?

641
01:24:48,230 --> 01:24:49,070
Djevojcica?

642
01:24:52,950 --> 01:24:54,190
Djecak?

643
01:24:55,870 --> 01:24:57,110
Ako si djecak,,
zašto ne bušiš?

644
01:24:59,310 --> 01:25:02,350
Bereš cvijece za vrijeme ovakve
krize!

645
01:25:03,550 --> 01:25:04,590
Hajde!

646
01:26:19,094 --> 01:26:23,454
Dobro! Dobro!
Problem je ovdje.

647
01:26:30,174 --> 01:26:31,254
Hej! Što to radiš!

648
01:26:41,198 --> 01:26:42,478
Povucite jako!

649
01:26:49,078 --> 01:26:49,998
Što to imaš?

650
01:26:50,198 --> 01:26:52,358
Uzeto od samuraja koji je bježao

651
01:26:54,078 --> 01:26:55,398
Gdje si to našao?

652
01:26:56,278 --> 01:26:57,198
U ovom selu?

653
01:26:57,398 --> 01:26:58,678
Kod Manzovih

654
01:27:09,495 --> 01:27:10,815
Ne dopadaju ti se?

655
01:27:13,175 --> 01:27:14,815
Lijep primjerak!

656
01:27:17,015 --> 01:27:21,615
Što nije u redu? Htio si
ove stvari, zar ne?

657
01:27:22,735 --> 01:27:23,895
Srami se!

658
01:27:30,907 --> 01:27:33,467
Skinuli su to sa ubijenog samuraja

659
01:27:34,147 --> 01:27:36,547
-Znam.
-Kako se usuðuješ...!

660
01:27:38,817 --> 01:27:41,657
Onaj koji nikada nije bio
lovina, ne bi razumio

661
01:27:54,857 --> 01:27:56,617
Odlazi! Nije ništa!

662
01:28:21,509 --> 01:28:25,629
Volio bih pobiti svakog
farmera u ovom selu!

663
01:28:40,142 --> 01:28:41,582
Dobra ideja!

664
01:28:44,782 --> 01:28:46,182
Hej, ti!

665
01:28:46,582 --> 01:28:48,382
Što mislite o farmerima?

666
01:28:49,222 --> 01:28:50,742
Svetci?

667
01:28:51,702 --> 01:28:52,822
Baš!

668
01:28:53,262 --> 01:28:55,862
Lukave su to životinje!

669
01:29:01,974 --> 01:29:06,534
Kažu: "Nemamo riže, nemamo
pšenice. Nicega nemamo!"

670
01:29:08,574 --> 01:29:10,294
Ali imaju!

671
01:29:10,974 --> 01:29:12,494
Imaju sve to!

672
01:29:13,774 --> 01:29:15,574
Prekopajte podove!

673
01:29:15,774 --> 01:29:17,494
Ili pretražite štale!

674
01:29:17,734 --> 01:29:19,414
Naci cete dosta toga!

675
01:29:19,574 --> 01:29:20,614
Riža!

676
01:29:21,014 --> 01:29:22,494
Sol! Mahunarke! Sake!

677
01:29:29,309 --> 01:29:31,029
Pogledajte u kanjone!

678
01:29:31,229 --> 01:29:32,429
Skrivene farme!

679
01:29:33,389 --> 01:29:36,629
Izdaju se za svetce, ali
su puni laži!

680
01:29:37,949 --> 01:29:40,549
Ako osjete borbu,
napadaju poražene!

681
01:29:43,229 --> 01:29:44,469
Slušaj!

682
01:29:44,789 --> 01:29:46,429
Farmeri su,

683
01:29:46,589 --> 01:29:49,669
cicije, lukave, cmizdrave

684
01:29:49,789 --> 01:29:53,109
zlobne, glupe ubojice!

685
01:29:55,102 --> 01:29:57,462
Zaboga!
Oni su takvi!

686
01:30:01,742 --> 01:30:04,302
Ali onda!
Tko je nacinio od njih takve zvijeri?

687
01:30:05,302 --> 01:30:08,182
Vi ste! Vi samuraji ste odgovorni!

688
01:30:17,662 --> 01:30:19,542
Vi im palite sela!

689
01:30:19,742 --> 01:30:21,102
Uništavate im farme!

690
01:30:21,262 --> 01:30:22,582
Kradete im hranu!

691
01:30:23,062 --> 01:30:24,982
Prisiljavate ih na mukotrpan rad!

692
01:30:25,182 --> 01:30:26,622
Otimate im žene!

693
01:30:27,102 --> 01:30:28,582
I ubijate ih ako pruže otpor!

694
01:30:28,742 --> 01:30:32,302
Pa što bi farmeri trebali raditi?

695
01:30:33,822 --> 01:30:36,622
Dovraga... Dovraga...

696
01:31:13,975 --> 01:31:16,775
Ti si sin farmera.
Zar ne?

697
01:31:55,192 --> 01:31:57,992
Da li... da li se nešto
desilo, gospodine?

698
01:31:58,672 --> 01:32:00,472
Ništa, Djede

699
01:32:00,672 --> 01:32:01,632
Sve je u redu

700
01:33:10,248 --> 01:33:13,208
Od veceras spavam ovdje

701
01:33:14,728 --> 01:33:16,928
Ne dopada mi se njihovo društvo

702
01:33:18,488 --> 01:33:19,648
Budalo!

703
01:33:20,208 --> 01:33:21,968
Nemoj se iskompleksirati!

704
01:33:22,488 --> 01:33:24,088
Je li ovo tvoj dom?

705
01:33:25,128 --> 01:33:27,808
Dao si im svoju kucu
a ti spavaš ovdje?

706
01:33:27,968 --> 01:33:29,248
Smrtno uplašen!

707
01:33:29,408 --> 01:33:30,328
Spavaj!

708
01:33:46,141 --> 01:33:47,781
Kao u stara dobra vremena

709
01:34:06,807 --> 01:34:08,247
Tako je mirno

710
01:34:11,574 --> 01:34:16,214
Ne mogu vjerovati da planine
vrve od razbojnika

711
01:34:18,254 --> 01:34:21,614
Sheeyit!
Kad bih sada imao ženu pored sebe...

712
01:34:30,254 --> 01:34:32,374
-Gdje?
-U planinu?

713
01:34:32,534 --> 01:34:33,454
Da vježbam

714
01:34:36,311 --> 01:34:37,791
Tamo nema žena!

715
01:34:39,711 --> 01:34:41,591
Nekada si zaista oštrouman

716
01:34:43,271 --> 01:34:44,831
Što to radiš?

717
01:34:45,751 --> 01:34:47,111
Našu zastavu

718
01:34:48,231 --> 01:34:49,671
U borbi,

719
01:34:50,231 --> 01:34:52,991
trebat ce nam nešto sa cime cemo mahati

720
01:34:58,311 --> 01:34:59,351
Što to znaci?

721
01:35:00,511 --> 01:35:04,351
Ovo znaci "Farma."
Farmeri. Ovo selo

722
01:35:06,848 --> 01:35:09,088
-Ovi krugovi?
-Mi

723
01:35:10,088 --> 01:35:11,848
Samo šest, a?

724
01:35:12,008 --> 01:35:13,248
Ja sam ispao?

725
01:35:14,288 --> 01:35:16,408
Trouga predstavlja vas,
gospodine. Kikuchiyo

726
01:36:39,071 --> 01:36:40,351
To je riža.

727
01:36:40,991 --> 01:36:43,031
-Pojedi.
-Ali...

728
01:36:43,111 --> 01:36:46,351
Probao sam proso po prvi put

729
01:36:47,791 --> 01:36:49,551
Užasno je

730
01:36:52,111 --> 01:36:53,911
Hajde

731
01:37:04,591 --> 01:37:07,311
Nemoj se sramiti.
Želiš biti sama?

732
01:37:08,271 --> 01:37:10,031
Ja necu jesti

733
01:37:10,231 --> 01:37:11,711
Zašto?

734
01:37:11,911 --> 01:37:12,831
Donio sam to za vas

735
01:37:13,071 --> 01:37:19,711
Radije bih to dala
Kyuemonovoj Baki

736
01:37:22,167 --> 01:37:23,727
Kyuemonova Baka?

737
01:37:45,647 --> 01:37:47,407
Sada nisam gladan

738
01:37:47,567 --> 01:37:48,847
Pojest cu to kasnije

739
01:37:50,383 --> 01:37:51,943
Jedi ti

740
01:37:52,823 --> 01:37:54,623
Sacuvat cu moje za kasnije

741
01:37:55,783 --> 01:37:58,623
Što se dešava?
Reci mi!

742
01:38:09,044 --> 01:38:10,684
Ovo je strašno

743
01:38:12,164 --> 01:38:13,644
Nema roðaka?

744
01:38:14,404 --> 01:38:16,644
Ne, gospodine. Razbojnici...

745
01:38:23,551 --> 01:38:29,391
Volio bih da mogu umrijeti ovog trenutka

746
01:38:29,951 --> 01:38:33,111
Hocu umrijeti uskoro,

747
01:38:33,271 --> 01:38:38,511
da pobjegnem iz ove bijede

748
01:38:40,870 --> 01:38:42,430
Ali, onda

749
01:38:43,430 --> 01:38:46,550
ce u svijetu koji nailazi,

750
01:38:46,830 --> 01:38:51,390
biti velika bijeda,
nažalost

751
01:38:54,367 --> 01:38:56,167
Nece!

752
01:38:56,527 --> 01:39:00,647
Nema rata, nema razbojnika
u sljedecem svijetu

753
01:39:00,927 --> 01:39:03,007
Nema ni bijede

754
01:39:03,367 --> 01:39:05,527
Kako znaš?
Da li si nekada bio tamo?

755
01:39:06,807 --> 01:39:08,207
Zašto se toliko dereš?

756
01:39:08,727 --> 01:39:10,727
Mrzim sve te proklete ljude!

757
01:39:10,887 --> 01:39:12,367
Gade mi se!

758
01:39:19,984 --> 01:39:21,624
Prokletstvo!

759
01:39:21,784 --> 01:39:23,424
Hocu napraviti nešto

760
01:39:23,584 --> 01:39:26,744
Sacuvaj ta osjecaje za razbojnike

761
01:39:42,504 --> 01:39:44,224
Zar nisi ti...

762
01:39:47,604 --> 01:39:49,884
Jesi li ti...

763
01:39:50,073 --> 01:39:55,033
Da li si me vidio danas,
tamo sa...

764
01:39:55,546 --> 01:39:56,066
Djevojkom?

765
01:39:56,746 --> 01:39:58,426
Da

766
01:39:58,666 --> 01:40:00,706
Zašto nisi rekao...?

767
01:40:00,866 --> 01:40:02,466
Da li to želiš?

768
01:40:17,186 --> 01:40:19,746
Daj nam malo riže!

769
01:40:20,706 --> 01:40:22,706
Daj nam bijele riže!

770
01:40:28,310 --> 01:40:28,990
Nemamo rižu!

771
01:40:35,590 --> 01:40:38,550
Nemojte se derati,
ogladnit cete

772
01:40:38,950 --> 01:40:41,710
Daj nam rižu!
Belu rižu!

773
01:40:45,826 --> 01:40:48,586
Slušajte vi derišta!

774
01:40:50,866 --> 01:40:53,066
Ovo je sve što vam možemo dati

775
01:40:53,146 --> 01:40:55,226
Ako vam damo više, mi cemo...

776
01:40:59,546 --> 01:41:00,906
Vidiš?

777
01:41:02,873 --> 01:41:05,073
Nego! Zar netko od vas nema zgodnu sestru?

778
01:41:08,553 --> 01:41:10,353
Bilo tko?

779
01:41:14,426 --> 01:41:17,626
Kada cete u žetvu?

780
01:41:18,329 --> 01:41:20,049
Za deset dana

781
01:41:20,129 --> 01:41:22,329
Koliko ce trajati ako budete radili
najbrže što možete?

782
01:41:24,249 --> 01:41:26,849
Najmanje tri dana.

783
01:41:28,009 --> 01:41:30,769
Hocu da se odmah posle poplavi polje

784
01:41:31,569 --> 01:41:33,969
Trebat ce nam jarak kod južne granice,

785
01:41:34,049 --> 01:41:36,329
tako da ni jedan konjanik ne može prici

786
01:41:36,409 --> 01:41:38,889
Jarak mora biti širok

787
01:41:39,769 --> 01:41:44,529
Pa, iskopat cemo kanal
i poplavit cemo farmu

788
01:41:44,609 --> 01:41:45,969
Posao ce biti obavljen za jedan dan

789
01:41:46,049 --> 01:41:47,769
Hvala

790
01:41:49,329 --> 01:41:51,409
Još jedna stvar

791
01:41:51,889 --> 01:41:54,769
Prve tri kuce i ovaj mlin

792
01:41:55,449 --> 01:41:57,849
moraju biti evakuirani
kada žetva bude završena

793
01:42:01,914 --> 01:42:03,474
Što? Mene evakuirati?

794
01:42:10,994 --> 01:42:12,154
Žao mi je

795
01:42:14,594 --> 01:42:15,954
Nema nam druge

796
01:42:19,066 --> 01:42:22,146
Ne možemo pokrivati ovako veliko podrucje

797
01:42:44,274 --> 01:42:45,274
Slušajte!

798
01:42:45,354 --> 01:42:47,394
Žetva samo što nije

799
01:42:47,594 --> 01:42:49,514
A onda ce razbojnici doci

800
01:42:49,794 --> 01:42:51,234
Budimo spremni

801
01:42:51,594 --> 01:42:53,154
Od sada moramo biti

802
01:42:53,434 --> 01:42:55,074
kao napeta puška

803
01:42:56,067 --> 01:42:58,867
Žetvu cemo vršiti u grupama a ne pojedinacno

804
01:43:00,307 --> 01:43:03,467
Od sutra cete živjeti u grupama

805
01:43:04,387 --> 01:43:08,427
Zapamtite! Krecete se kao grupa a ne kao pojedinci.

806
01:43:11,287 --> 01:43:12,727
Muškarci, slušajte!

807
01:43:14,334 --> 01:43:17,574
Obilno volite svoje žene veceras

808
01:43:39,159 --> 01:43:41,799
To je glupo!

809
01:43:41,879 --> 01:43:43,959
Hajde, susjedi!

810
01:43:47,919 --> 01:43:49,199
Bacite ih!

811
01:43:49,319 --> 01:43:53,799
Necemo preuzimati rizik
da bismo zaštitili ostale!

812
01:43:54,806 --> 01:43:55,926
Hajde!

813
01:43:56,006 --> 01:43:57,806
Zaštitimo naše vlastite domove!

814
01:44:00,246 --> 01:44:01,326
Stani!

815
01:44:04,966 --> 01:44:08,526
Uzmite koplja!
Vratite se na položaje

816
01:44:46,788 --> 01:44:49,108
Gdje je Yohei?
Ta prokleta budala!

817
01:44:54,451 --> 01:44:56,091
Budalo!

818
01:45:15,101 --> 01:45:17,141
Samo su tri kuce izvan sela

819
01:45:18,021 --> 01:45:19,661
Selo ima dvadeset kuca

820
01:45:20,781 --> 01:45:24,221
Ne možemo ugroziti dvadeset kuca zbog tri!

821
01:45:25,821 --> 01:45:29,861
Kuce izvan sela ne mogu biti spašene

822
01:45:30,661 --> 01:45:32,301
dok vlasništvo sela uništavaju!

823
01:45:37,709 --> 01:45:38,869
Zapamtite!

824
01:45:39,269 --> 01:45:40,589
To je rat!

825
01:45:42,429 --> 01:45:44,549
Svi ste u istom camcu!

826
01:45:47,149 --> 01:45:52,429
Onaj tko misli samo na sebe
bit ce takoðer uništen!

827
01:45:55,069 --> 01:45:58,429
Takva sebicnost se nece trpjeti!

828
01:47:15,857 --> 01:47:18,257
Sheeyit! Tko bi samo pomislio

829
01:47:24,827 --> 01:47:26,267
Tolike žene su živjele ovdje!

830
01:47:27,240 --> 01:47:29,360
Gdje ste skrivali ove djevojke?

831
01:47:41,884 --> 01:47:43,604
Daj mi svoj srp!

832
01:47:44,324 --> 01:47:46,364
Nasjeci cu i za tebe

833
01:47:46,604 --> 01:47:49,004
Da budemo dobri prijatelji, a?

834
01:48:14,820 --> 01:48:15,780
Rikichi!

835
01:48:17,220 --> 01:48:20,180
Vidim da su oni u braku najproduktivniji

836
01:48:21,380 --> 01:48:23,180
Volio bi kada bi se oženio

837
01:48:27,620 --> 01:48:28,980
Zašto se ljutiš?

838
01:48:29,060 --> 01:48:30,500
Samo sam htio...

839
01:48:31,740 --> 01:48:34,060
Katsushiro, dovedi ga nazad!

840
01:48:34,260 --> 01:48:35,820
Zašto je pobjegao?

841
01:48:45,916 --> 01:48:47,156
Shino, prestani sanjariti!

842
01:49:05,108 --> 01:49:07,428
Što je ovo?
Medvjeða jazbina?

843
01:49:10,108 --> 01:49:11,828
Požnjeveno je

844
01:49:14,548 --> 01:49:15,628
Rikichi, a?

845
01:49:16,948 --> 01:49:18,388
Nisam vidio

846
01:49:18,668 --> 01:49:20,668
Baš sam ga tražio, kada je izašao

847
01:49:20,748 --> 01:49:25,348
Njegovo lice je bilo znojavo i odavalo je napetost.

848
01:49:30,462 --> 01:49:31,782
Što si mu rekao?

849
01:49:32,102 --> 01:49:35,262
Ništa.
Samo sam mu predložio da se oženi.

850
01:49:38,702 --> 01:49:43,102
Nešto veoma bolno ga izjeda

851
01:49:43,182 --> 01:49:44,902
Njegovo lice mi to govori

852
01:49:46,222 --> 01:49:51,222
Njegova usta su zapecacena

853
01:49:51,862 --> 01:49:53,582
Pokušaj ih otvoriti

854
01:50:02,526 --> 01:50:03,566
Tko je tamo?

855
01:50:03,646 --> 01:50:04,726
Ja sam!

856
01:50:07,006 --> 01:50:09,326
Da li je sve u redu?

857
01:50:16,566 --> 01:50:18,126
Želiš li sjesti?

858
01:50:18,526 --> 01:50:20,086
Popricajmo

859
01:50:26,389 --> 01:50:31,669
Cesto se dešava da prica smiruje
uznemiren um

860
01:50:32,589 --> 01:50:36,229
Prica o patnji je olakšavanje

861
01:50:39,709 --> 01:50:42,709
Uzgred, ti si covjek koji malo govori

862
01:50:44,758 --> 01:50:48,118
Ali, ako držiš nešto u sebi

863
01:50:48,478 --> 01:50:49,958
najbolje je da to pustiš van

864
01:50:51,998 --> 01:50:55,638
I vjerujem da nema boljeg trenutka
za to od ovog

865
01:50:57,518 --> 01:50:59,358
Sa mnom je sve uredu

866
01:51:18,213 --> 01:51:19,293
Hajmo van

867
01:51:22,053 --> 01:51:24,653
Nemoj ga buditi.
On je dijete

868
01:51:34,134 --> 01:51:35,854
Rekao je "Shino."

869
01:51:36,254 --> 01:51:37,654
Shino je...

870
01:51:39,134 --> 01:51:41,054
Žensko ime

871
01:51:41,174 --> 01:51:43,974
Ne izgleda kao djecji san

872
01:51:49,774 --> 01:51:51,574
Odakle cemo poceti?

873
01:51:52,334 --> 01:51:54,454
Prije svega, od najslabijeg.

874
01:52:53,765 --> 01:52:54,805
Tko je tamo?

875
01:53:01,725 --> 01:53:02,845
Tko je tamo?

876
01:53:03,525 --> 01:53:04,685
Izaði!

877
01:53:05,885 --> 01:53:06,965
Tko je tamo?

878
01:53:07,045 --> 01:53:08,005
Kikuchiyo!

879
01:53:10,685 --> 01:53:12,125
Imaš srece!

880
01:53:13,165 --> 01:53:15,445
Da je bio razbojnik,
tvoja glava...

881
01:53:49,118 --> 01:53:50,158
Yohei!

882
01:53:51,598 --> 01:53:52,638
Što je ovo?

883
01:53:53,798 --> 01:53:55,238
Moj konj, gospodine

884
01:53:57,958 --> 01:54:00,038
Pomislio sam da je to debeli miš

885
01:54:40,718 --> 01:54:48,398
Vrapci pjevaju, vrane grakcu

886
01:54:53,533 --> 01:54:56,013
