Zar razbojnici ne dolaze?

887
01:54:58,653 --> 01:55:00,853
Ako ne doðu, bit ce to veliki gubitak!

888
01:55:01,773 --> 01:55:03,693
Unajmiti te pohlepne samuraje!

889
01:55:03,973 --> 01:55:07,253
-Budalo!
-Najbolje bi bilo da se razbojnici uopce ne pojave!

890
01:55:15,069 --> 01:55:18,109
Što ceš sa tim starim konjem?

891
01:55:24,036 --> 01:55:26,716
Stani! Yohei ce plakati ako ga obogaljiš!

892
01:55:27,196 --> 01:55:29,676
O cemu pricaš?
Ja sam dobar jahac!

893
01:55:42,516 --> 01:55:43,476
Dobar je!

894
01:55:59,574 --> 01:56:00,854
To izgleda dobro!

895
01:56:25,638 --> 01:56:26,798
Sretni su

896
01:56:29,078 --> 01:56:31,478
Žetva je završena a nema znaka od razbojnika

897
01:56:32,158 --> 01:56:34,838
Pocinju misliti da nitko nece doci

898
01:56:36,758 --> 01:56:38,878
Kad bi tako bilo

899
01:56:39,318 --> 01:56:43,998
Opasnost vreba onda kada sve
izgleda sigurno

900
01:56:46,310 --> 01:56:48,310
Recite im da zauzmu svoje položaje!

901
01:57:22,447 --> 01:57:25,327
Voljela bih da sam samurajeva kcer

902
01:57:29,238 --> 01:57:31,158
Proklet je farmerski život

903
01:57:32,158 --> 01:57:35,238
Ja sam previše sretan. Sram me je

904
01:57:35,598 --> 01:57:37,158
Nisam tako mislila

905
01:57:37,918 --> 01:57:40,598
Ti si samuraj a ja seljanka

906
01:57:40,958 --> 01:57:41,798
Nikada nisam...

907
01:57:42,118 --> 01:57:43,798
O, ne smeta mi!

908
01:57:43,878 --> 01:57:47,118
Ne brinem se za buducnost!

909
01:58:23,528 --> 01:58:24,688
Kukavice!

910
01:58:24,768 --> 01:58:26,008
Zar ti nisi samuraj?

911
01:59:33,767 --> 01:59:36,087
Tri stranca,
blizu zapadnog puta, gospodine

912
01:59:38,687 --> 01:59:41,567
-Nitko ništa ne zna za ovo.
-Za sada

913
01:59:41,647 --> 01:59:42,727
Budimo tihi

914
01:59:45,807 --> 01:59:48,487
Vidio sam tri konja na brdu!

915
01:59:48,647 --> 01:59:49,687
Razbojnici!

916
01:59:50,007 --> 01:59:51,167
Znam

917
01:59:56,918 --> 01:59:58,838
-Ovdje su!
-Kako znaš?

918
01:59:59,318 --> 02:00:01,918
Ocigledno je. Sve ovo komešanje

919
02:00:05,758 --> 02:00:07,958
Iz kojeg pravca?
Brda ili sa zapada?

920
02:00:10,478 --> 02:00:11,518
Sa zapada

921
02:00:20,238 --> 02:00:21,198
Razbojnici dolaze!

922
02:00:26,551 --> 02:00:27,791
Recite im da ostanu unutra

923
02:00:27,911 --> 02:00:29,591
Samo ih je trojica

924
02:00:29,751 --> 02:00:31,471
Neka budu tihi

925
02:00:32,471 --> 02:00:34,111
Mora da su izviðaci

926
02:00:34,391 --> 02:00:35,711
Ne smiju nas vidjeti

927
02:00:54,470 --> 02:00:55,990
Što je bilo?

928
02:01:01,270 --> 02:01:02,310
Banditi?

929
02:01:03,030 --> 02:01:04,390
Jesu li došli?

930
02:01:16,032 --> 02:01:16,992
Tišina!

931
02:01:19,112 --> 02:01:20,072
Gdje?

932
02:01:21,112 --> 02:01:22,552
Ono drvo...!

933
02:01:38,446 --> 02:01:40,286
Nesumnjivo izviðaci

934
02:01:41,286 --> 02:01:42,846
Izgledaju iznenaðeno zbog ograde.

935
02:01:44,206 --> 02:01:46,566
Ne znaju da smo ovdje

936
02:01:46,646 --> 02:01:48,566
Nadam se da si u pravu

937
02:01:52,847 --> 02:01:53,967
Gdje su svi?

938
02:01:54,047 --> 02:01:55,127
Kakva budala!

939
02:01:56,647 --> 02:01:57,927
Kikuchiyo!

940
02:02:04,607 --> 02:02:05,767
Jesu li došli?

941
02:02:05,847 --> 02:02:06,607
Jeli tako?

942
02:02:10,007 --> 02:02:11,247
Sada su nas vidjeli!

943
02:02:23,672 --> 02:02:26,232
Ne smiju otici sada kada znaju

944
02:02:27,912 --> 02:02:30,032
Ubit cu ih.
Na mojoj su teritoriji

945
02:02:31,072 --> 02:02:32,192
Nisam znao...

946
02:02:32,272 --> 02:02:35,552
Kreni. Uhvati jednoga da izgladiš stvar

947
02:02:36,072 --> 02:02:37,672
Idi precicom

948
02:02:37,912 --> 02:02:39,552
Da, do konja

949
02:02:42,391 --> 02:02:43,631
Katsushiro!

950
02:02:44,831 --> 02:02:45,871
Ti samo promatraj! Razumiješ?

951
02:02:55,048 --> 02:02:56,688
Dobri konji!

952
02:03:01,208 --> 02:03:02,848
Ti lezi ovdje

953
02:03:11,608 --> 02:03:13,248
-Što ceš napraviti?
-Ja?

954
02:05:15,375 --> 02:05:18,535
Katsushiro! Gotovo je

955
02:05:19,095 --> 02:05:20,375
Izaði

956
02:05:44,495 --> 02:05:48,695
Cekaj! Ovo je ratni zarobljenik!

957
02:05:49,415 --> 02:05:54,935
Moli za milost!
Ne smijemo ga ubiti

958
02:05:55,072 --> 02:05:55,832
Ne treba nam vaša pomoc!

959
02:06:22,200 --> 02:06:26,280
Pusti je da osveti smrt svoga sina!

960
02:06:27,144 --> 02:06:28,504
Neko!

961
02:06:29,104 --> 02:06:30,424
Pomozi joj!

962
02:06:40,624 --> 02:06:43,104
Ako je vjerovati razbojniku, njihovo
utvrðenje mora da je...

963
02:06:43,184 --> 02:06:45,504
-Slabo!
-Sigurno je puno rupa

964
02:06:45,784 --> 02:06:47,704
kao Yoheijeve hlace!

965
02:06:47,984 --> 02:06:49,264
Ako je tako pristupacno

966
02:06:49,344 --> 02:06:51,424
-Napadnimo.
-Njih je cetrdeset

967
02:06:51,944 --> 02:06:53,944
Moramo im smanjiti broj

968
02:06:55,024 --> 02:06:57,024
ako je moguce bez
gubitaka sa naše strane

969
02:06:57,104 --> 02:06:59,184
Ne možemo si priuštiti da izgubimo nekoga

970
02:06:59,264 --> 02:07:00,944
Svaka bitka je kocka

971
02:07:01,024 --> 02:07:03,064
Troje može ubiti najmanje desetoricu

972
02:07:08,215 --> 02:07:11,095
Da li je to mjesto daleko?

973
02:07:11,255 --> 02:07:12,495
Jedan dan hoda

974
02:07:13,255 --> 02:07:15,575
Ali sada imamo konje!

975
02:07:15,735 --> 02:07:17,175
Onda pola dana

976
02:07:29,735 --> 02:07:30,775
U redu!

977
02:07:31,535 --> 02:07:34,015
Ako sada krenemo, stici cemo u zoru.

978
02:07:34,295 --> 02:07:35,535
Ali tko?

979
02:07:40,026 --> 02:07:40,866
Ti ne!

