1224
03:01:32,652 --> 03:01:33,892
Onda cu ja uzeti ovo

1225
03:01:39,467 --> 03:01:40,547
Shino!

1226
03:01:43,083 --> 03:01:44,243
Shino!

1227
03:02:06,392 --> 03:02:09,192
Evo ti sake.
Pij i odmori se

1228
03:02:14,940 --> 03:02:16,380
Ovo ne lici na tebe

1229
03:02:16,660 --> 03:02:18,300
Budi neustrašiv i bori se snažno!

1230
03:03:26,199 --> 03:03:27,279
Shino!

1231
03:03:37,519 --> 03:03:38,839
Ti ljencino!

1232
03:03:56,638 --> 03:03:57,878
Nemoj bjesnit!

1233
03:03:57,958 --> 03:04:01,038
Kako to misliš,
zaljubila se u samuraja?

1234
03:04:40,415 --> 03:04:41,255
Manzo!

1235
03:04:42,695 --> 03:04:44,815
Je li ovo tvoja kcerka?

1236
03:04:51,701 --> 03:04:52,941
Reci mi!

1237
03:04:53,821 --> 03:04:56,781
Rekao si da se zaljubila u samuraja.
Na što si mislio?

1238
03:04:59,381 --> 03:05:00,421
Manzo!

1239
03:05:10,799 --> 03:05:12,159
Progovori!

1240
03:05:13,927 --> 03:05:14,887
Reci nam!

1241
03:05:47,713 --> 03:05:48,953
Jesi ti Shino?

1242
03:06:08,809 --> 03:06:09,969
Manzo!

1243
03:06:10,409 --> 03:06:11,849
Nemoj se ljutiti!

1244
03:06:13,409 --> 03:06:16,009
Kada covjek vidi smrt
kako mu se približava,

1245
03:06:16,329 --> 03:06:18,249
osjeca potrebu za
ženskim rukama,

1246
03:06:26,161 --> 03:06:28,401
pred bitku

1247
03:06:30,361 --> 03:06:32,561
Tako se radi i u dvorcu!

1248
03:06:36,161 --> 03:06:39,041
Imaj obzira za mlade!

1249
03:06:41,041 --> 03:06:42,401
Ne mogu!

1250
03:06:43,521 --> 03:06:45,441
Moja kcer je zavedena!

1251
03:07:01,026 --> 03:07:02,546
Ali se vole!

1252
03:07:03,146 --> 03:07:05,146
I nisu je odveli razbojnici!

1253
03:08:38,154 --> 03:08:39,594
Svi su i odviše nervozni

1254
03:08:40,154 --> 03:08:41,434
Opusti se!

1255
03:08:50,937 --> 03:08:53,537
Svi. Najzad,
odlucujuca bitka!

1256
03:08:56,857 --> 03:08:58,377
Uzgred, Katsushiro!

1257
03:08:58,657 --> 03:09:00,457
Bori se hrabro!

1258
03:09:02,577 --> 03:09:04,777
Sada si odrastao covjek!

1259
03:09:23,672 --> 03:09:24,632
Hej!

1260
03:09:28,072 --> 03:09:29,112
Hej!

1261
03:09:29,352 --> 03:09:30,712
Pokažite zube!

1262
03:09:32,977 --> 03:09:35,497
Sa takvim izrazima lica necete osvojiti bitku!

1263
03:09:50,416 --> 03:09:52,776
Kikuchiyo, što to pobogu radiš?

1264
03:09:52,856 --> 03:09:54,416
Ne mogu ih sve pobiti
jednim macem!

1265
03:10:10,865 --> 03:10:12,345
Ostala su samo trinaestorica!

1266
03:10:13,865 --> 03:10:17,625
Pustite ih sve unutra!

1267
03:10:19,545 --> 03:10:21,465
Odmah cemo ih opkoliti

1268
03:10:22,385 --> 03:10:25,265
I uhvatiti u klopku na prijelazu!

1269
03:10:29,240 --> 03:10:32,400
Ova borba ce pokazati ishod!

1270
03:11:03,577 --> 03:11:05,497
Stižu!

1271
03:11:28,713 --> 03:11:30,273
Stižu!

1272
03:11:55,657 --> 03:11:57,377
Shichirogi, Katsushiro Zapad!

1273
03:11:57,977 --> 03:11:59,617
Kyouzo, Kikuchiyo Istok!

1274
03:13:41,622 --> 03:13:43,182
Katsushiro! Rikichi!

1275
03:13:43,542 --> 03:13:44,822
Katsushiro!

1276
03:13:45,582 --> 03:13:46,742
Idi na istok!

1277
03:14:06,885 --> 03:14:07,845
Šuti!

1278
03:14:09,085 --> 03:14:10,245
Ili ceš umrijeti!

1279
03:14:58,211 --> 03:15:00,171
Odlicno. Dobro obavljeno!

1280
03:14:59,949 --> 03:15:01,549
Uspio sam ! Uspio sam!

1281
03:15:01,749 --> 03:15:03,469
Ustani!
Idi na istok!

1282
03:15:19,431 --> 03:15:21,271
Katsushiro... Ustani

1283
03:15:21,991 --> 03:15:23,431
Budi oprezan

1284
03:15:24,151 --> 03:15:26,351
Proklet bio! Dovraga!

1285
03:15:28,365 --> 03:15:29,685
Kikuchiyo!

1286
03:16:18,702 --> 03:16:19,942
Razbojnici!

1287
03:16:20,022 --> 03:16:21,382
Razbojnici!

1288
03:16:21,462 --> 03:16:22,622
Svi su mrtvi!

1289
03:16:42,135 --> 03:16:43,935
Opet smo preživjeli

1290
03:20:23,271 --> 03:20:26,911
Opet smo poraženi

1291
03:20:31,311 --> 03:20:32,831
Oni farmeri su pobjednici

1292
03:20:35,031 --> 03:20:36,311
A ne mi

